<h1>Affiliates Index</h1>

<p>Hi. This is your access point to student affiliates, run by students, for the students</p>

<p>Not only are we committed to helping you succeed, we are also passionate about ensuring we create opportunities throughout the year for you to grow, succeed and have fun.</p>

<p>We make it our mission to provide students with a range of activities, opportunities and services.</p>

<p>Becoming a member of an affiliate, means you will have the security of knowing there is someone looking out for you and putting your interests first</p>

<table class ="listing" summary="Affiliates list">
  <tr class="header">
    <th>Alphabetical</th>
  </tr>
  <% @affiliates.each do |affiliate| %>
    <tr>
      <td><%= link_to("#{affiliate.title}", affiliate_path(affiliate), :class => 'action show') %></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
